/** Device short cut */
1. Please insmod the dsc driver, command is "insmod dsc.ko"
2. We can do configuration to the "/proc/dsc/dsc_config" interface
3. For setting the WAN interface(e.g. eth2), please run
    echo wan-add eth2 > /proc/dsc/dsc_config
4. For setting the LAN interface(e.g. eth2), please run
    echo lan_add eth2 > /proc/dsc/dsc_config
5. For enabling the PPPOE passthrough, please run
    echo pppoe 1 > /proc/dsc/dsc_config
6. For setting the LAN IP address(e.g. 192.168.0.1, in hex format ), please run
    echo lan_ip c0a80001 > /proc/dsc/dsc_config

